is a problem for me.

16:04.430 --> 16:06.398
- But I didn't think that.
- It's just time to go.

16:06.465 --> 16:08.956
Please, just listen to me.
Just give me one second.

16:09.034 --> 16:10.126
No, I don't have a second.

16:10.202 --> 16:12.329
Okay, can I just
say something, please?

16:12.404 --> 16:13.336
What?

16:13.405 --> 16:15.236
I didn't do the crime.

16:15.307 --> 16:17.002
You rude mother...

16:19.311 --> 16:20.801
I ain't goin'.

16:44.503 --> 16:48.633
It's your baby,
Peter, and don't you deny it!

16:48.707 --> 16:51.369
That DNA test told on you!

16:51.443 --> 16:53.468
You lie, Peter!

16:53.545 --> 16:55.877
You know lil' Kareem is yours!

16:56.982 --> 16:58.142
Why?!

16:58.217 --> 17:00.082
