like that, Peter?!

17:00.152 --> 17:04.555
You told me I was your
beautiful African Queen.

17:04.623 --> 17:07.147
And I loved you
for that, Peter!

17:07.226 --> 17:09.217
I didn't care if your
little thing was curved.

17:10.695 --> 17:13.096
And lil' Kareem don't want
your child support.

17:13.165 --> 17:17.124
He just want a relationship
with his white daddy.

17:18.737 --> 17:20.704
A little
chocolate/vanilla swirl

17:20.772 --> 17:23.173
from that magical night
at the crackhouse.

17:23.242 --> 17:23.833
Oh!

17:25.544 --> 17:28.012
Come on.
Just be quiet!

17:28.079 --> 17:30.310
Wait just a second.
My shoes.

17:30.382 --> 17:32.009
- Mr. Sanderson?
- Whoa!

17:32.084 --> 17:33.312
Is everything okay?

17:33.385 --> 17:35.785
I thought I heard Negro.

17:35.854 --> 17:39.517
No. No Negro spoken here.

17:39.591 --> 17:41.650
Oh.

17:41.727 --> 17:44.696
Well... good night, then.

17:44.763 --> 17:46.958
Oh, uh...

17:47.032 --> 17:48.397
good night.

17:53.105 --> 17:54.265
Come on!

17:54.339 --> 17:56.000
Come on, come on!

17:59.411 --> 18:02.107
You stay. You stay.
You wait right there.

18:02.181 --> 18:04.149
Who you callin'?

18:04.216 --> 18:05.979
The police.

18:07.753 --> 18:10.221
Police department.
Sergeant Panella. Please hold.

18:10.289 --> 18:11.449
What's that?

18:11.523 --> 18:13.013
It's all of our e-mails.

18:13.092 --> 18:15.026
You think anybody at Tobias,
Kline, and Barnes

18:15.094 --> 18:16.686
would be interested
in hearing

18:16.762 --> 18:19.322
about you looking for Boom-boom
in the federal pen?

18:20.365 --> 18:22.026
And I'll send a photo.

18:22.101 --> 18:23.625
