Can I help you?

18:28.440 --> 18:31.568
Now, this is just
for tonight, understand?

18:35.747 --> 18:37.715
A'ight.

18:37.783 --> 18:40.047
I can work with this.

18:40.119 --> 18:42.246
But, uh, look,
don't be gettin' no ideas

18:42.321 --> 18:44.755
about sneakin' up in here
and hittin' this ass,

18:44.823 --> 18:47.417
