with this fine sister.

18:47.493 --> 18:49.723
Dare to dream.

18:49.795 --> 18:51.888
Tsk. Please.

18:56.101 --> 18:58.365
Oh, my God! A bed!

18:58.437 --> 19:01.235
Oh, a nice, big, cushy bed.

19:01.306 --> 19:03.900
Ohh, no roommates,
no cellmates.

19:21.293 --> 19:22.624
Charlene?

19:24.329 --> 19:25.796
Charlene.

19:28.934 --> 19:31.596
Charlene! Come on,
you're not fooling anybody.

19:32.871 --> 19:35.101
Who that? Who there?

19:35.174 --> 19:36.937
Who want it with Lene?

19:38.377 --> 19:40.277
